    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with a stout platform and plenty of upside for the right buyer. The engine fires up and the car presents as a solid candidate for someone who appreciates proven mechanical fundamentals and doesn\u2019t mind putting in some finishing work. Chassis feels like a good starting point, and it has the kind of honest, usable character that makes it worth saving rather than parting out. Not a showroom piece, but a compelling budget entry for an enthusiast looking for a fixer with real potential. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 7900.0,
