    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn presence that turns errands into little adventures. It\u2019s not trying to be showroom perfect\u2014it\u2019s the sort of machine for someone who appreciates character, possibility, and a vehicle with a story already written into it. A great fit for a hands-on owner, a budget-minded commuter, or anyone looking for an inexpensive set of wheels with personality and potential.",
      "price": 5900.0,
