      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right owner? This one is a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a handy runabout, or a project to make their own. It\u2019s not perfect, but it starts, goes, and offers real value for the money. If you\u2019re after something cheap, usable, and worth a look, this could be the one.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project with strong enthusiast potential. The powertrain fires up and pulls with respectable torque, and the chassis still feels like a worthwhile platform for someone who knows their way around maintenance and sorting. Cosmetically it shows age and needs attention, but the fundamentals are there: usable interior, complete body, and a drivetrain that offers a good starting point for a budget build, daily beater, or shop truck. If you want an affordable entry point with room to improve, this one has the kind of mechanical character that makes it worth a look.",
      "price": 7900.0,
